{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 264\u2089 to base 10**\n264\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070\n= 2\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 4\u00d71\n= 162 + 54 + 4\n= 220\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 374\u2089 to base 10**\n374\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070\n= 3\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 4\u00d71\n= 243 + 63 + 4\n= 310\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n220\u2081\u2080 \u00d7 310\u2081\u2080 = 68,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 68,200\u2081\u2080 to base 9**\n68,200 \u00f7 9 = 7,577 R 7 \u2192 Check: 7,577\u00d79 + 7 = 68,193 + 7 = 68,200 \u2713\n7,577 \u00f7 9 = 841 R 8 \u2192 Check: 841\u00d79 + 8 = 7,569 + 8 = 7,577 \u2713\n841 \u00f7 9 = 93 R 4 \u2192 Check: 93\u00d79 + 4 = 837 + 4 = 841 \u2713\n93 \u00f7 9 = 10 R 3 \u2192 Check: 10\u00d79 + 3 = 90 + 3 = 93 \u2713\n10 \u00f7 9 = 1 R 1 \u2192 Check: 1\u00d79 + 1 = 9 + 1 = 10 \u2713\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 R 1 \u2192 Check: 0\u00d79 + 1 = 1 \u2713\n\nRemainders (top to bottom): 7, 8, 4, 3, 1, 1\nReading bottom to top: 113487\u2089\n\n**Step 5: Verify**\n113487\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u2075 + 1\u00d79\u2074 + 3\u00d79\u00b3 + 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070\n= 1\u00d759,049 + 1\u00d76,561 + 3\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 7\u00d71\n= 59,049 + 6,561 + 2,187 + 324 + 72 + 7\n= 68,200\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n113487", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 716}